Motivation behind looking at college vs NFL
College sports in general have a higher turnover of players
Players transfer to other schools or leave early to play professionally
There are 32 teams in the NFL vs. ~250 Division I college football teams
Therefore NFL games are usually busy and, while one might expect the top ranked college stadiums to be busy, what about the other 200?
